.spuyt
  .history
    h3 Short history of Volleybalvereniging De Spuyt
    p In 1983 a group of enthusiastic volleyball player regularly met in café De Spuyt. They played against each other for a long time and there was no discussion regarding a club, but it started slowly to itch. There was a need for actual competition! This resulted in the creation of De Spuyt volleyball club on 31 August 1987.
  
